    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior still holds a great shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and all electronics functioning as intended. It drives smoothly and represents a solid, dependable option for its next owner.",
